---------------------------------------------
Project: BOMJINIKA Kernel
Authors: Enzo / Gabriel
Language: C (100%)
Platform: x86_64
Boot: UEFI (M0+) → Native (M1+)
License: Apache 2.0
---------------------------------------------

The BOMJINIKA Kernel is an open-source, pure C operating system kernel
designed for modern x86_64 architecture. It aims to be minimal,
modular, and fully transparent — every single component is written in C,
with no external languages or hidden layers.

Core principles:
 - 100% C source code
 - Portable architecture
 - Transparent and open development
 - Focused on performance, stability, and simplicity

